  "title": "Administrative Executive",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Assist in handling for the overall general office administrative duties;</li><li>Support and responsible for the office supplies and project purchasing, claim;</li><li>Support HR department and functions;</li><li>Assist in Social medica and Company branding matters;</li><li>Exhibition booth design, preparation and participation;</li><li>Perform any other duties as assigned by the Manager.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or equivalent and preferably specialized in Business management/Marketing.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and MS Excel</li><li>Positive attitude, good interpersonal and organisational skills</li><li>Proficient in English and Mandarin, required for effective coordination with China headquarters, overseas technical teams, and China-based clients.</li><li>Able to hands-on, multitask and work independently</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Takes initiative, fast learner and adaptable to dynamic situations</li><li>Immediate availability preferred</li></ul>",
