  "postedCompany": {
    "uen": "T15FC0014F",
    "description": "<p>CREG - China Railway Engineering Equipment Group Co., Ltd. - is a leading TBM supplier with a capacity to manufacture up 280 metro-size TBM per year. Headquartered in the center of China, CREG provides full-range TBM solutions together with its up-to-date technical solutions highly oriented towards project challenges and customer expectations. As of now, CREG has manufactured over 1000 TBMs and bored through more than 2000km of tunnels. Other than China, CREG has also established its presence in 21 countries. CREG is able to produce all types of TBM namely EPB TBM, Slurry TBM, Single/double-shield TBM, Gripper TBM and multi-mode TBM with boring dia. ranging from 3 m to 16 m. These TBMs have achieved exceptional performances and are highly appreciated by customers worldwide. This speaks of CREG's strong commitment to provide technical assistance and manufacturing quality at the highest level. Other than TBM manufacturing, CREG also produces a wide range of auxiliary tunneling equipment such as shaft boring machine, drilling jumbo, roadheader, disc cutters, locomotives, rollign stocks as well as tunneling formworks and building structures. CREG Singapore Branch - Subsidiary of CREG China – is established in 2015 to render full support for Southeast Asia region particularly the after sales service. To date, CREG has supplied over 30 TBMs in Singapore and all of the projects have been successfully completed.</p>",
    "name": "CHINA RAILWAY ENGINEERING EQUIPMENT GROUP CO., LTD. Singapore Branch",
